---

<div class="pb-32">
  <Sectionhead>
    <Fragment slot="title">Works with your technologies</Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="desc">
        Supporting every Linux based machine, bare-metal, vanilla VM, Kubernetes.
      </Fragment>
    <!-- <h2 class="text-center text-slate-500">Works with your technologies</h2> -->
